  "320:319": {
    "inputs": {
      "value": "Animate the person in the reference image with natural, confident, and elegant posing movements. The subject subtly shifts their posture, turns slightly toward the camera, and smoothly raises one arm to showcase the accessory or product they are wearing, such as a watch, bracelet, ring, bag, or clothing detail. Add a gentle hand gesture and a brief, natural glance toward the featured item before looking back at the camera.\n\nKeep the subject’s face, identity, hairstyle, body proportions, outfit, accessories, and background consistent with the original image. Use realistic body mechanics, subtle facial expressions, natural blinking, and smooth hand movements. The camera performs a slow cinematic push-in with slight parallax, creating a premium fashion-commercial look. Maintain realistic lighting, sharp details, stable composition, and smooth motion.\n\nAvoid exaggerated movements, facial distortion, identity changes, warped hands, extra fingers, disappearing accessories, sudden camera movement, flickering, unnatural body motion, or changes to the original environment.\n"
    },
